.red} [yellow]{ .yellow} [blue]{ .blue} [green]{ .green} [red]{ .red}.› 

This leads me to pick up the _Sorcery Handbook and Introduction with Primer
on Porting Ink, 14th Edition_ I've been carrying around since two days ago,
without even being able to read the title. I look up 'hailing' without reading
